            "descriptionRaw": "Throws out a Floral Ring that deals 1 instance of <color=#99FF88FF>Dendro DMG</color> to targets it comes into contact with.\nThe Floral Ring will return after a set time, dealing <color=#99FF88FF>Dendro DMG</color> once again.\n\n<i>This is Collei's go-to gadget for dealing with unruly wild beasts. A few good thwacks from this tool will generally improve their behavior. This same principle works just as well on evildoers.</i>",
            "name": "Floral Brush"
        },
